Installation:

    git clone git://n7700/vim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
jsdlhlskghl

Adding bundles from repos:
    git submodule add http://github.com/oscarh/vimerl.git bundle/vimerl
